{"lastModified":1775127504099,"uri":"c::39480359087::vessel::19df18f0-e7ba-11f0-aa37-0fbc44ed5cd4","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sicily, Italy, Sardinia, Naples, Malta, Calabria, Gulf of Naples, Taormina, Amalfitanian Coast\n\nFairline 55 Fly is a 17 meters timeless flybridge motor yacht equipped with twin 715 hp D-12 Volvo Penta engines that offers both speed and smooth cruising. \n\nThe large flybridge offers plenty of space for relaxing, entertaining and sunbathing while the interior provides 3 cabins to comfortably accommodate 6 guests overnight (1 Master and 1 VIP with double bed, and 1 Twin cabin with separate beds), plus 1 cabin, 2 berths, crew with head. All cabins include ensuite bathrooms and individually managed climate zones.\n\nThe aft deck is equipped with a large table for al fresco dining and is the ideal place to enjoy breakfast. At the bow there is a sunbathing area with a folding table. Further moments of relaxation can be spent on the upper deck with panoramic views of the sea.","blueprint":{"name":"FAIRLINE 55 FLY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::19df18f0-e7ba-11f0-aa37-0fbc44ed5cd4::assets::b75e16b0-e7bc-11f0-b096-5be3d91a22dd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::19df18f0-e7ba-11f0-aa37-0fbc44ed5cd4::assets::b75e8be0-e7bc-11f0-b096-5be3d91a22dd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::19df18f0-e7ba-11f0-aa37-0fbc44ed5cd4::assets::b75d0540-e7bc-11f0-b096-5be3d91a22dd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::19df18f0-e7ba-11f0-aa37-0fbc44ed5cd4::assets::b75d5360-e7bc-11f0-b096-5be3d91a22dd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::19df18f0-e7ba-11f0-aa37-0fbc44ed5cd4::assets::b75f0110-e7bc-11f0-b096-5be3d91a22dd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::19df18f0-e7ba-11f0-aa37-0fbc44ed5cd4::assets::b75eda00-e7bc-11f0-b096-5be3d91a22dd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::19df18f0-e7ba-11f0-aa37-0fbc44ed5cd4::assets::b75eb2f0-e7bc-11f0-b096-5be3d91a22dd/{imageV